1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>不管怎样，是时候发表我的年度技术乐观主义帖子了，我在其中大肆宣传一些我感到兴奋的技术领域。当然，这并不是一份详尽的清单，但它列出了主要亮点。我在底部列出了往年的综述，这样你就可以查看我往年提到的内容，并确定我的兴奋是否合理。</p><p> <em>（<strong>财务披露</strong>：我投资了几家与这篇文章中的技术相关的初创公司，包括<a href="http://impulselabs.com/">一家电池供电的电器公司</a>、<a href="https://brev.dev/">一家将人工智能公司与云提供商连接起来的公司</a>、一家<a href="https://bytez.com/">开源人工智能初创公司</a>以及一家为机器人制造机器人的公司。药物测试。如果我找到一个好的公司，我想投资一家制造消费机器人的初创公司！）</em></p><h4>机器人世界来了</h4><p>许多感叹 2010 年代看似渐进的进步的人会抱怨我们没有得到 1960 年代动画片<em>《杰森一家》</em>中所设想的未来。通常这指的是我们没有飞行汽车这一事实。但重要的是要记住， <em>《杰森一家》</em>中描绘的大多数技术实际上都是某种类型的机器人——最著名的是打扫家里的机器人女仆。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg" width="706" height="353" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:369,&quot;width&quot;:738,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:706,&quot;bytes&quot;:45724,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc81c55cc-dc03-47f0-8873-a0ae7868e94c_738x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这项技术可以说比飞行汽车更具变革性和乌托邦色彩。<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/time-use">调查显示</a>，大多数国家的人们平均每天花 2 至 3 小时在家务和购物上——可能占我们清醒时间的八分之一。除了没有报酬之外，这几乎是我们最不喜欢的消磨时间的方式： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg" width="590" height="890.5529411764705" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c67f2ace-bebc-4ab4-95df-aec517dca479_850x1283.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quo