/div></div></figure></div><p>对于<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1743594071929844164">奇幻插画</a>来说，他们几乎可以与所有在世的人类艺术家媲美。</p><p>我对人工智能艺术比法学硕士更乐观的原因是训练数据的可用性。<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2211.04325.pdf">维拉洛博斯等人。 （2022）</a>表明，高质量的语言数据将在 2020 年代初到中期耗尽（假设没有合成数据），但图像数据直到 2040 年代才会耗尽： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg" width="1345" height="557" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:557,&quot;width&quot;:1345,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:228241,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2211.04325.pdf">Villalobos 等人。 (2022)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>新的图像数据（至少在某些类型上）比高质量的人类生成的语言数据更容易生成——只需派出一堆无人机去拍摄数万亿张照片即可。</p><p>因此，尽管人工智能艺术正在变得越来越好，但我认为它有潜力以惊人的速度不断变得更好。焦点已经从静态图像转移到<a href="https://medium.com/@artturi-jalli/ai-video-generators-14312e5bcb62">视频生成</a>。显然，随着深度造假视频的激增，这会给我们的信息生态系统带来一些问题——一些人认为深度造假可能已经<a href="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/slovakia-election-deepfakes">影响了斯洛伐克的选举</a>。但是，让每个人都可以轻松生成逼真的视频，这绝对会改变生活。 （我可能会用它来制作<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1744661100774449292">巨型兔龙</a>的电影。） </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg" width="636" height="636" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:900,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:636,&quot;bytes&quot;:246824,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;DRACARROTS.&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="DRACARROTS." title="龙胡萝卜。" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><h4>电池的十年仍在继续</h4><p>我<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/decade-of-the-battery">一直非常乐观的</a>一项技术是电池。这是因为电池代表了人类以前从未真正拥有过的东西——一种存储大量能量并随身携带的方式。</p><p>就其本身而言，存储方面就非常重要。人们越来越多地使用电池作为解决方案来消除太阳能和风能的间歇性，在夜间、雨天甚至冬季提供稳定的电力供应。在世界各地，电网电力的电池存储正在呈指数级增长。 EIA<a href="https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=61202">预计美国的这一数字将接近翻倍</a>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg" width="1151" height="738" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:738,&quot;width&quot;:1151,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:147012,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F43da597b-09b2-4668-87c3-4e228cd03b3e_1151x738.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=61202">环境影响评估</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>尽管言论保守，但美国德克萨斯州却是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/blue-states-dont-build">可再生能源发电量最大的</a>州，该州正在<a href="https://www.expressnews.com/business/article/ercot-record-year-adding-texas-battery-sites-come-18580143.php">增加大量</a>电池。</p><p>甚至在我们考虑可移植性之前，储存能量的能力除了平滑可再生电力之外还有大量的应用。例如，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/battery-powered-appliances">我投资的</a>电池供电电器公司Impulse Labs刚刚发布了它的第一款产品——超级动力炉子——现在正在<a href="https://shop.impulselabs.com/products/impulse-induction-cooktop-tier1">接受预订</a>。 </p><div id="youtube2-r0U3mTAiV-k" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;r0U3mTAiV-k&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/r0U3mTAiV-k?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p> （他们也在<a href="https://twitter.com/sdamico/status/1744913020923572725">招聘</a>。）</p><p>但电池的重要性不仅仅限于存储；电池还使能源<em>变得便携</em>，这意味着它们可以与柴油和汽油等液体燃料竞争。彭博新能源财经<a href="https://twitter.com/CoreyBCantor/status/1572542277385605121">现在预测</a>，到 2020 年代末，电动汽车将占美国新乘用车销量的一半以上。全球范围内<a href="https://about.bnef.com/electric-vehicle-outlook/">的转型也将是迅速的</a>，这在很大程度上要归功于中国，中国已大幅提高电动汽车产量并成为世界上最大的汽车出口国。这会引起<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/car-wars">贸易摩擦</a>，但最终对环境和消费者满意度都有好处。</p><p>当然，电池也是上述初期机器人革命的幕后推手。他们也在改变天空。无人机正在证明自己是<a href="https://www.wsj.com/world/drones-everywhere-how-the-technological-revolution-on-ukraine-battlefields-is-reshaping-modern-warfare-bf5d531b">现代战争的重要武器</a>（正如<a href="https://qz.com/185945/drones-are-about-to-upheave-society-in-a-way-we-havent-seen-in-700-years">我很久以前预测的</a>那样），而小型电池供电的四轴飞行器无人机是其中的关键部分。当然，无人机也将在各种<a href="https://www.inspiredflight.com/news/top-10-commercial-uses-for-drones.php">和平应用</a>中发挥作用，但军事领域的革命似乎是目前最重要的。</p><p>而电池最令人惊奇的是，其基础技术还远未成熟。两项巨大的创新刚刚进入商业化阶段：钠离子电池和固态电池。</p><p>固态电池<a href="https://www.uk-cpi.com/blog/6-ways-solid-state-batteries-are-better-than-lithium-ion-alternatives-in-electric-vehicles">在各方面都比我们现在使用的电池更好</a>——它们更轻、更小、更强、更安全、续航里程更大、充电更快，而且对环境更有利。丰田即将<a href="https://insideevs.com/news/697474/toyota-solid-state-ev-small-numbers/">开始销售配备固态电池的汽车</a>；我们将拭目以待，但我的猜测是，十年内<em>有人</em>将成功地将固态电池商业化。</p><p>与此同时，钠离子电池具有<a href="https://www.iberdrola.com/sustainability/environment/energy-efficiency/sodium-ion-batteries">很多性能优势</a>，并且比锂离子电池使用的稀有金属少得多。中国公司目前正在将其用于<a href="https://www.energy-storage.news/world-first-grid-scale-sodium-ion-battery-project-in-china-enters-commercial-operation/">电网存储</a>，也<a href="https://news.yahoo.com/sodium-ion-batteries-gaining-traction-150000318.html">可能用于电动汽车</a>。</p><p>尽管电池革命目前令人惊叹，但它才刚刚开始。</p><h4>生物技术仍然蓬勃发展</h4><p>我们通常认为生物技术与电气和机械应用领域的创新截然不同，但两者正在开始融合。一般来说，计算对于现代药物发现和化学至关重要，而人工智能看起来将成为<a href="https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.ade2574">另一个重要工具</a>。与此同时，生物实验越来越多地在实验室中使用机器人。</p><p>但<a href="https://twitter.com/DKThomp/status/1740057506506997967">目前正在展开的</a>生物技术革命不仅仅是其他技术的下游——它是数十年大量工作和雄厚资金投资的结果，现在正在取得成果。</p><p> mRNA 疫苗是新冠病毒大流行的英雄，现在正被应用于许多其他疾病。一种新的<a href="https://www.the-scientist.com/news/a-new-mrna-malaria-vaccine-71533">疟疾 mRNA 疫苗</a>有望帮助战胜人类最致命的慢性疾病。一种针对<a href="https://www.nih.gov/news-events/nih-research-matters/mrna-vaccine-treat-pancreatic-cancer">胰腺癌的新型 mRNA 疫苗</a>（实际上是在确诊<em>后</em>而不是之前进行治疗）有望挽救来自这种最致命癌症之一的大量生命。 <a href="https://www.cedars-sinai.edu/research/news/cedars-science/2022/experimental-vaccine-for-brain-cancer.html">其他癌症</a>可能也可以通过这种方式治疗。</p><p>另一项刚刚实现的技术是基因工程，特别是通过 CRISPR。 FDA 刚刚批准了一种药物，该药物实际上可以进入并<a href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/biotech/fda-approves-worlds-first-crispr-gene-editing-drug-for-sickle-cell-disease-8c65fbb3">重新设计活人体内的细胞</a>来治疗镰状细胞性贫血。其他此类药物正在<a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41392-023-01309-7">研发中</a>。基因工程也被证明可用于改造细菌和其他生物体以达到有用的目的，例如<a href="https://interestingengineering.com/innovation/ai-improves-genome-editing-of-microbes-to-produce-renewable-fuels">生产燃料</a>或<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37053311/">对抗癌症</a>。当然，所有这一切都是在重新设计人类本身的潜力之外，但这仍然是<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2023/09/11/the-transformative-alarming-power-of-gene-editing">在地平线上</a>。</p><p>合成生物学是第三个主要技术领域，其潜力仍在显现，但可能在不久的将来实现。今年，科学家合成了 DNA 来制造<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/11/09/synthetic-biology-yeast-artificial-genome">人造酵母细胞</a>。合成生物学最终可以用来创造各种定制的生物体来完成各种工作。</p><p>我还应该向我在 Loyal 公司的朋友们表示感谢，他们<a href="https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-new-drug-that-could-extend-dogs-lives-inches-closer-to-approval-180983331/">即将获得 FDA 批准</a>第一种用于狗的商业长寿药物。我希望这些药物对宠物兔子有用，或者他们制作兔子版本。</p><p>但今年<a href="https://www.science.org/content/article/breakthrough-of-the-year-2023#section_breakthrough">最重要的生物技术发现</a>有点出乎意料。一类被称为 GLP-1 激动剂的药物，包括 Ozempic、Wegovy 和 Mounjaro，长期用于治疗糖尿病，已被证明在帮助人们减肥方面非常有效。肥胖流行病是美国第一大健康问题，并且正在蔓延到世界其他地区。这些药物是对抗这种流行病的第一个真正有效的药物方法。</p><p>最重要的是，这些药物治疗肥胖的<em>方法</em>之一——基本上是减少对食物的渴望——也<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/ozempic-might-help-you-drink-and-smoke-less-a2354ce7">使得它们有助于</a>对抗各种其他成瘾行为，如酗酒和吸烟。这使得它们成为解决困扰先进社会的许多弊病的潜在改变者。由于巨大的需求，对这些药物的需求已经<a href="https://www.wsj.com/economy/central-banking/americas-obsession-with-weight-loss-drugs-is-affecting-the-economy-of-denmark-22797e5c">推动了丹麦的经济发展</a>，丹麦是生产 Ozempic 和 Wegovy 的公司的所在地。</p><p>所以无论如何，生物技术的承诺似乎在这十年里确实以各种非常棒的方式实现了。</p><h4>重新征服太空</h4><p>2020 年代尚未发挥作用的最重要发明之一是 SpaceX 的星际飞船，这是一种比土星五号还要大的巨型可重复使用火箭，看起来像 1930 年代漫画书中的火箭飞船，而且可以廉价大量制造。星舰还没有成功飞行，但每次测试都越来越近了。看起来非常雄伟： </p><div id="youtube2-C3iHAgwIYtI" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;C3iHAgwIYtI&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/C3iHAgwIYtI?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>星际飞船似乎极有可能在十年内变得可用，之后很多目前不可能的太空事物<a href="https://caseyhandmer.wordpress.com/2021/10/28/starship-is-still-not-understood/">将变得可行</a>——小行星采矿、太空制造、火星基地等等。事实上，火箭还可以非常快速地跳跃并降落在地球上的其他地方，这使其成为一种非常有用的快速运输方式。在我们经历阿波罗事件后的长期撤退之后，星际飞船比任何其他技术都更有希望将人类带回太空。这一次，我们将留在那里。</p><h4>以前的年度技术乐观帖子</h4><p>以下是这篇文章过去几年的版本，所以你可以看看我的乐观是否成功。到目前为止，我认为我的希望很少破灭。 </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;f101ba35-4a21-4a86-becc-2672e2767452&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;When I started this new Substack blog, I wanted to make it explicitly techno-optimist. The 2010s felt like a decade in which many Americans &#8212; especially in intellectual circles &#8212; undervalued and dismissed the promise of technology, deriding it as &#8220;solutionism&#8221;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Techno-optimism for 2023&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2022-12-12T07:50:00.859Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F681c7531-2605-4215-ad45-ac53eab96618_900x900.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-2023&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:89088675,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:230,&quot;comment_count&quot;:94,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69