ll,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:683,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:82624,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fa03297-fb0f-4bfa-af7e-7ed45879790a_1024x683.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fa03297-fb0f-4bfa-af7e-7ed45879790a_1024x683.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fa03297-fb0f-4bfa-af7e-7ed45879790a_1024x683.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fa03297-fb0f-4bfa-af7e-7ed45879790a_1024x683.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/14214150@N02/48636817606">“埃塞俄比亚联合利华口腔护理工厂的一名工人”，</a> <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/14214150@N02">DFID - 英国国际发展部</a>， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/?ref=ccsearch&amp;atype=rich">CC BY 2.0</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>我今天从台湾飞回来！我以前在飞机上写作，但座位太窄，所以我的生产力降低了。那好吧。因此，这里是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/all-futurism-is-afrofuturism">来自 Noahpinion 档案的转贴</a>。</p><p>这些天，非洲几乎不再出现在美国的新闻中。但如果你想想本世纪剩下的时间，以及未来会是什么样子，你就不可能不去想世界第二大大陆。简而言之，有两个原因：1）人口，2）贫困。非洲的生育率正在下降，就像其他地方一样，但它开始下降的时间要晚得多。因此，人口增长势头将使非洲人口在达到顶峰时变得非常庞大（一些预测者认为这将在本世纪末左右发生）。以下是<a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/fandd/issues/2023/09/PT-african-century">国际货币基金组织报告</a>中的信息图： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg" width="670" height="887.657967032967" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1929,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:670,&quot;bytes&quot;:586311,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/fandd/issues/2023/09/PT-african-century">国际货币基金组织</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>您会注意到这些估计值比我在下面的文章中的第一张图中的估计值低很多。这是因为非洲生育率的<a href="https://www.economist.com/middle-east-and-africa/2023/04/05/the-worlds-peak-population-may-be-smaller-than-expected">下降幅度远远</a>超出了人们的预期。但即使按照这些较低的估计，到本世纪末非洲预计仍将是绝对庞大的。而且其<em>年轻</em>人口的比例还要高得多。不久之后，世界各国将会大声疾呼非洲移民，而不是试图将他们拒之门外。</p><p>非洲重要的另一个原因是贫困。现在很明显，非洲将成为世界上最后一个无法维持最低生活水平的主要地区。它是否以及如何摆脱这种命运的问题是下面帖子的主题。但请注意，贫困的另一面是<em>潜在的</em>；贫穷意味着你有很大的成长空间，到本世纪末，大多数劳动密集型任务可能会在非洲完成。</p><p>增长实际上表现良好。尽管人们都在谈论脱钩和中国经济大幅放缓，尽管西方媒体偶尔<a href="https://t.co/u4C1Bwng3x">会感到不安</a>，但撒哈拉以南非洲地区的增长在 2022 年和 2023 年<a href="https://twitter.com/MssZeeUsman/status/1742286799379050759?t=YlwU8i-yVJfWeV21milztg&amp;s=19">仍然相当强劲</a>。预计今年这种情况还将继续： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg" width="900" height="506" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:506,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:133459,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4351ec-1be9-4e29-b486-d19c0c47ca55_900x506.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：国际货币基金组织，来自<a href="https://twitter.com/MssZeeUsman/status/1742286799379050759?t=YlwU8i-yVJfWeV21milztg&amp;s=19">Zainab Usman</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>请注意，随着人口增长放缓，这些收益将通过人口<a href="https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/fandd/2006/09/basics.htm">红利</a>日益转化为更高的人均生活水平。</p><p>所以无论如何，非洲对我们的未来仍然非常重要，我仍然对此持谨慎乐观的态度。这是我三年前写的：</p><div><hr></div><p>时不时地，我就有在博客上写一些真正重要的事情的冲动，所以今天我想我会写一些关于非洲的文章。</p><p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrofuturism">非洲未来主义</a>是科幻小说和哲学的一个有趣的子流派：，但每次看到这个词我都会咯咯笑，因为<em>所有</em>未来主义实际上都是非洲未来主义。非洲实际上是整个世界的未来。<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/future-population-growth">这</a>是您将看到的两三个最重要的图表之一： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-a