00vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>请注意，这是对<em>总</em>人口的预测。到本世纪末，非洲的人口数量将与亚洲人口持平，但如果我们只看<em>年轻</em>人口，非洲将占据明显的多数。</p><p> “等等，”你可能会问。 “这些 80 年的预测真的可靠吗？如果非洲生育率下降怎么办？”</p><p>答案是：要掉下来了！已经在快速下降了。随着国家变得更加富裕，生育率下降；正如莱曼·斯通 (Lyman Stone) 所表明的那样，相对于其收入水平，非洲的生育率下降速度比除印度以外的任何其他地区都要快： </p><div data-component-name="Twitter2ToDOM" class="tweet" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/lymanstoneky/status/1052558799372877824&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;People have asked me to show the data that African fertility is NOT high compared to its income.\n\nThis is real GDP per capita vs total fertility rate by region, World Bank data. I've marked where unusually high/low TFR countries should fall. &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;lymanstoneky&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Lyman Stone &#30707;&#20358;&#27665;&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Wed Oct 17 13:55:48 +0000 2018&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/DptwpWbUYAAXo1r.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/4w0nKBzXfd&quot;}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:104,&quot;like_count&quot;:186,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{},&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"><a class="tweet-link-top" href="https://twitter.com/lymanstoneky/status/1052558799372877824" target="_blank"><div class="tweet-header"><img class="tweet-header-avatar" src="https://substackcdn.com/image/twitter_name/w_96/lymanstoneky.jpg" alt="@lymanstoneky 的 Twitter 头像" loading="lazy"><div class="tweet-header-text"><span class="tweet-author-name">莱曼石 石来民</span><span class="tweet-author-handle">@lymanstoneky</span></div></div><div class="tweet-text">人们要求我展示非洲生育率与其收入相比并不高的数据。这是世界银行数据，按地区划分的实际人均国内生产总值与总生育率的对比。我已经标记了生育率异常高/低的国家/地区应该下降的位置。 </div><div class="tweet-photos-container one"><div class="tweet-photo-wrapper "><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_600,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.substack.com%2Fmedia%2FDptwpWbUYAAXo1r.jpg"><img class="tweet-photo" src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_600,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.substack.com%2Fmedia%2FDptwpWbUYAAXo1r.jpg" alt="图像" loading="lazy"></picture></div></div><a class="tweet-link-bottom" href="https://twitter.com/lymanstoneky/status/1052558799372877824" target="_blank"><div class="tweet-footer"><span class="tweet-date">下午 1:55 ∙ 2018 年 10 月 17 日</span><hr><div class="tweet-ufi"><span href="https://twitter.com/lymanstoneky/status/1052558799372877824/likes" class="likes"><span class="like-count">186 点</span>赞</span><span href="https://twitter.com/lymanstoneky/status/1052558799372877824/retweets" class="retweets"><span class="rt-count">104</span>转发</span></div></div></div><p>这是非洲人口最多的七个国家的图片。尽管尼日利亚、刚果民主共和国和坦桑尼亚仍处于早期阶段，但您已经可以看到生育率转变正在发生。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F15931757-dfdd-4278-866c-cf2ee5d61dbc_648x426.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F15931757-dfdd-4278-866c-cf2ee5d61dbc_648x426.png 424w, https://subst