—在很长一段时间内非常漫长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg" width="1185" height="573" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ebfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:573,&quot;width&quot;:1185,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:158559,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Febfdaa7c-a9eb-46a3-b1b3-549826894ec2_1185x573.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">原文来源：Natalia Bronshetein</figcaption></figure></div><p>与西班牙裔一样，爱尔兰移民大多是工薪阶层，他们来到这里主要是出于经济原因——来自爱尔兰贫困的压力，以及在美国取得成功的伟大梦想。和西班牙裔一样，他们激起了本土主义者持续而猛烈的抵制。</p><h4>都是一样的烦恼</h4><p>这篇文章顶部的漫画<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970203430404577096851689671274">来自 1871 年</a>，其中包含大量负面刻板印象——爱尔兰人是恐怖分子、酒鬼、罪犯、试图主宰美国文化。</p><p>对爱尔兰人的担忧往往特别集中在宗教角度——作为天主教徒，爱尔兰人对教皇心存感激，要么会颠覆和摧毁美国的民主自由，要么会屠杀新教徒。 1800 年代初爆发了针对爱尔兰人的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philadelphia_nativist_riots">恶性屠杀</a>。但以下是约翰·海厄姆 (John Higham) 的<em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Strangers-Land-Patterns-American-1860-1925/dp/0813531233">《异乡人》 (Strangers in the Land)</a></em>中的几段截图，显示天主教徒和新教徒之间对种族战争和种族灭绝的焦虑至少持续到了 1890 年代： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg" width="538" height="338" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ab18476b-7af7-41f0-8c9c-68bb15520ea8_538x338.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageS