b-455d-4c55-ad6b-97f71f6fa187_535x377.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa02d517b-455d-4c55-ad6b-97f71f6fa187_535x377.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa02d517b-455d-4c55-ad6b-97f71f6fa187_535x377.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa02d517b-455d-4c55-ad6b-97f71f6fa187_535x377.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>你可以看到这些焦虑与现代保守派对西班牙裔移民的担忧并行。保守派担心<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/american-border-crisis-invites-terrorists-to-attack-c7f154bc">恐怖分子正从南部边境涌入</a>，担心美国传统文化会被移民文化<a href="https://newcriterion.com/issues/2021/12/unprecedented">摧毁</a>，甚至担心美国会发生<a href="https://theconversation.com/america-is-on-the-brink-of-another-civil-war-this-one-fuelled-by-donald-trump-210937">种族内战</a>。</p><p>经济问题也非常相似。阅读广田秀隆 (Hidetaka Hirota) 的书《 <em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Expelling-Poor-Atlantic-Nineteenth-Century-Immigration/dp/019061921X">驱逐穷人》(Expelling the Poor)</a></em> ，了解这一情况在 1800 年代初期是如何发生的。人们担心贫穷的爱尔兰移民会淹没当地的福利系统——类似于 20 世纪 90 年代及以后对西班牙裔人的福利国家超负荷的担忧——导致州一级出台了大量限制性反移民措施。这些在很大程度上失败了，因为爱尔兰移民通常会找到通过不同州进入的方式，但它们表明美国从来都不是一个开放边界的国家。</p><p>最重要的是政治担忧。由于爱尔兰移民通常投票支持民主党，联邦党人和辉格党政客担心他们在政治上被取代。以下是 Daniel Tichenor 的<em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dividing-Lines-Immigration-International-Perspectives/dp/0691088055">《分界线》</a></em>中的几段截图： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbaa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg" width="660" height="196.4957264957265" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/baa5ec05-484c-4579-b31d-8e08051a359b_702x209.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:209,&quot;width&quot;:702,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:660,&quot;bytes&q