ressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg" width="692" height="586.816" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:848,&quot;width&quot;:1000,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:692,&quot;bytes&quot;:267717,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff9db11f-360b-432b-bcaa-a84bec38b599_1000x848.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.census.gov/library/stories/2023/03/domestic-migration-trends-shifted.html">人口普查局</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>为什么会发生这种情况？考虑到从阳光明媚的加利福尼亚州<a href="https://myutk.maps.arcgis.com/apps/instant/sidebar/index.html?appid=b6cf315a28aa4089873ee3442d4a2597%27">搬到</a>寒冷的爱达荷州和蒙大拿州，这显然不仅仅是天气的问题。保守派倾向于将这一趋势归咎于蓝州的<a href="https://taxfoundation.org/data/all/state/state-population-change-2022/">高税收</a>和进步的社会政策。但对于大多数从一个地方搬到另一个地方的人来说<a href="https://fiscalpolicy.org/housing-costs-not-taxes-drive-migration-out-of-new-york">，住房成本在经济上比税收重要得多</a>。</p><p>加利福尼亚州和纽约州等蓝州的住房成本较高，部分原因是这些州往往拥有硅谷、好莱坞和华尔街等“超级明星”产业集群。这些集群吸引了高收入知识工作者，却让低收入和中等收入人群望而却步。但加州<a href="https://twitter.com/ShaneDPhillips/status/1737146341888016829">各个收入水平的人口都在流失</a>，高收入者实际上更有可能离开。更重要的是，如果蓝州愿意，他们可以为低收入和中等收入人群<em>建造更多房屋</em>，从而抵消需求增加的影响。</p><p>他们不这样做。除了华盛顿州（您会注意到，预计该州不会失去任何国会席位！）之外，蓝州在建造住房数量方面往往受到更多限制： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg" width="686" height="606.375" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1287,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:686,&quot;bytes&quot;:295202,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc198ba7c-c61e-4423-b99e-a9bb407e9c8f_1632x1443.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：人口普查，来自<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/dataisbeautiful/comments/zckw2a/oc_building_permits_in_housing_units_per_capita/">u/born_in_cyberspace</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>我不会重述允许更多住房供应可以降低住房成本的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-left-nimby-canon">证据</a>。<a href="https://kevinerdmann.substack.com/p/housing-supply-costs-and-urban-value-85a">确实如此</a>。加利福尼亚州和纽约州因拒绝建造足够的住房而将人们赶出该州，而德克萨斯州和佛罗里达州则以新的廉价住房欢迎新移民。</p><p>事实上，蓝州不允许发展是其政治文化的普遍特征。住房短缺不仅导致人口流失，也是席卷加州和纽约的无家可归浪潮的主要原因。进步人士声称对无家可归者的关心完全被他们拒绝允许在他们居住的地方附近建造新家园所抵消。住房并不是蓝州唯一未能建造的东西——反发展政治正在阻止蓝州采用太阳能和风能，而红州则领先。而红州愿意建造新工厂意味着进步的产业政策实际上让他们受益更多。</p><p>如果蓝州想要在 21 世纪蓬勃发展，他们需要重新学习如何建设、建设、建设。</p><h4>为什么红色州正在赢得绿色能源竞赛</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/blue-states-dont-build">阅读更多</a></p>;
